LINK: http://uppit.com/v/O0CGKGEV Please post comments. . .I have 136, but i need more ideas on what to add...
GOAL: 100 downloads. GOAL: 200 downloads. GOAL: 500 downloads. GOAL: 1,000 downloads.
EDIT: I'm going to be adding corporeal beast, and the shields. Only 83 downloads and 11 comments. . .(Some of witch are mine...)
What's in this? This is Lin's "Interface maker." Why am I posting it here? It has varois interface's in it that I have added along with a ID list. I take no credit's in this. I added this becuase it started out with barley any, so I hope this helps some of you find what your looking for. NOTE: If you want me to add something to it just comment, also I'm taking pictures on EVERYTHING in it and posting it so you can also see the quatily of everything and such.
I didn't show a picture of most of the BIG interfaces. But other than that here is the picture:) [URL=http://img202.imageshack.us/i/interfacepackpicture.png/][IMG]http://img202.imageshack.us/img202/3509/interfacepackpicture.th.png[/img][/URL]
